2958:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          *  list.  It will not block until the scheduler is unlocked - at which
2959:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          *  time a yield will be performed.  If an item is added to the queue while
2960:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          *  the queue is locked, and the calling task blocks on the queue, then the
2961:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          *  calling task will be immediately unblocked when the queue is unlocked. */
